.IX Subsection "value"
Returns the specified constant.
.SH "NAME"
SQL::Statement::ColumnValue \- term for column values
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 5
\&  # create a term with an SQL::Statement object as owner
\&  my $term = SQL::Statement::ColumnValue\->new( $owner, \*(Aqid\*(Aq );
